{"id":608110,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【立此存照】发现手机中装有vpn-给予行政处罚警告/","date":"2019-03-27T10:30:13Z","modified":"2019-03-27T10:30:13Z","title":"【立此存照】发现手机中装有VPN 给予行政处罚警告","content":"<p>3月27日，有推友分享了一份“蓬溪县公安局行政处罚决定书”。决定书中写道：“我队在工作中发现（未写明是技术手段发现还是检查手机发现但从描述上看较可能是后者）庞某手机中有VPN翻墙软件（无界一点通），依据《中华人民共和国计算机信息网络国际联网管理暂行规定》，对‘使用非法定信道进行国际联网’行为，给予行政处罚警告。”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-608122\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2qGkYJU4AAjCAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2qGkYJU4AAjCAM.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2qGkYJU4AAjCAM-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2qGkYJU4AAjCAM-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"BCE63y30wp\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bf%bb%e5%a2%99%e5%b7%b2%e6%88%90%e8%bf%9d%e6%b3%95%e8%a1%8c%e4%b8%ba%ef%bc%9f%e6%8a%93%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e7%bd%9a%e4%b8%80/\">【立此存照】“翻墙”已成违法行为？抓一次罚一千</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%bf%bb%e5%a2%99%e5%b7%b2%e6%88%90%e8%bf%9d%e6%b3%95%e8%a1%8c%e4%b8%ba%ef%bc%9f%e6%8a%93%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e7%bd%9a%e4%b8%80/embed/#?secret=BCE63y30wp\" data-secret=\"BCE63y30wp\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" title=\"《【立此存照】“翻墙”已成违法行为？抓一次罚一千》—中国数字时代\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"WICSdf1tn4\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/chinese-police-punish